  "excerpt": "<p>Once you\u2019re enrolled in a health plan and your coverage has started, you can use it to help cover medical costs for services</p>",
  "content": "<p><span>Knowing how to use your health coverage is important for better health and well-being. Health coverage isn\u2019t only important when you\u2019re sick, it\u2019s also helpful even when you don\u2019t feel sick.</span></p><p><span>After your health plan coverage starts, you can use it to help cover medical costs for services like:</span></p><ul><li><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"/using-marketplace-coverage/prescription-medications\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"920723c4-2867-4f3c-afe6-939e7a155b77\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"36861\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"Getting prescription medications\">Filling a prescription at the pharmacy</a></li><li><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"/using-marketplace-coverage/getting-medical-care\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"0e6b6ddf-ea67-490e-8c20-9b3b73722dd4\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"36851\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"Getting regular medical care\">Going to the doctor</a></li><li><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"/using-marketplace-coverage/getting-emergency-care\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"20a59268-208c-4ad4-bac8-4de7b49e8abc\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"36846\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"Getting emergency care\">Getting emergency care</a></li></ul><h2>Keep up with your health</h2><ul class=\"ul1\"><li class=\"li9\"><span class=\"s5\"><strong>Before your appointment</strong>: </span><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"/using-marketplace-coverage/improving-your-health\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"83c68194-1bad-4bc1-99c3-cab264cc4d2c\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"36856\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"Finding resources on staying healthy\"><span class=\"s5\">Get a refresher on using your coverage and improving your health</span></a><span class=\"s6\">.</span></li><li class=\"li11\"><span class=\"s6\"><strong>After your appointment</strong>: </span><span class=\"s7\">If you don\u2019t agree with a coverage or payment decision by your health plan, </span><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"/using-marketplace-coverage/appealing-insurance-company-decisions\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"2b324355-0f35-439f-850e-e5cd1315e4b7\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"36836\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"Appealing an insurance company decision \"><span class=\"s7\">you may be able to appeal</span></a><span class=\"s7\">.</span></li></ul><p class=\"p12\"><strong>Not sure if your coverage started?</strong> <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"/apply-and-enroll/complete-your-enrollment\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"65636127-2a63-4f89-ac7e-004b529a7a23\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"37251\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"Complete your enrollment &amp; pay your first premium\">Find out what to do if you don\u2019t have your insurance card</a>.&nbsp;</p><div class=\"box-content information-lightweight\"><div class=\"content\">Have Medicaid or coverage through the Children's Health Insurance Program (CHIP)?<br><a href=\"/medicaid-chip/using-medicaid-or-chip-coverage\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-uuid=\"f54f0ea6-3c3c-466a-a573-352f9f2fe3fc\" data-entity-id=\"37821\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"Using your new Medicaid or CHIP coverage\">Learn how to use your new Medicaid or CHIP coverage.</a></div></div><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"/get-answers\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"1204165e-6281-45d5-bfc8-c966812fe894\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"39366\" data-entity-bundle=\"landing_page\" title=\"How can we help you?\">Get answers to popular health insurance questions.</a></p>",
